{
  "stem": "8527.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I think it was-- the marriage was sort of fixed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- So how did the butcher shop come about to be a non-kosher butcher shop?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I don't know, that I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would imagine it was a business decision.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was less competition in the area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And perhaps they felt that this was the best way to make a living.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I don't-- you know, there was a lot of kosher butcher shops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, my grandfather was a butcher, and some of my uncles had butcher shops.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my-- my mother's sister, aunt-- I had an aunt-- I have an-- I had an aunt, she also had a butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I don't know how that came about, probably for business reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I do remember going into the butcher shop all the time, in fact, carrying meats out, delivering, seeing people come on the [POLISH] on their horse-drawn wagons, park in front of the store.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I also remember the-- that started happening in 1939 or so, where Poles would come and paste stickers on the customers' back with a sign saying, swinia-- swinia in Polish meaning pig-- for buying from Jews.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then on the other hand, the religious people didn't like us having treyf meat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was always a conflict.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how it got started, but I just happen to remember that now that you mention that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a conflict with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But our home life, I think, was fairly normal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have any wants or needs for anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had uncles that used to make toys for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'd gladly give them my food, and they would trade me for-- for toys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, I remember one thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
